Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.67,0:00:57.62,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Good evening everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.62,0:01:00.30,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(635.429,670)}Sakura Gakuin's homeroom teacher, \NMori Hayashi here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.30,0:01:04.20,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You might be wondering \Nwhat's happening right now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.20,0:01:08.20,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(572.571,664.286)}Well, this is actually a pre-recorded video
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.80,0:01:11.42,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,This is not live
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.42,0:01:18.47,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(580.571,676.857)}Or more accurately, this video right here is currently being broadcasted live
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.47,0:01:20.25,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Why, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.72,0:01:28.52,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Today is Obon so we'll be doing \Na ghost-themed episode
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.70,0:01:32.17,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(614.857,671.143)}So we're thinking of pranking the girls
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.42,0:01:38.37,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(518.858,674.572)}You might've already gotten used to seeing only them getting pranked, and so, for this episode...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.45,0:01:42.32,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(565.714,663.143)}we'll be having this person as the instigator
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.40,0:01:48.00,Marin,,0,0,0,,Hello! Stand Out! Chairperson, \NHidaka Marin here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:50.25,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(604.571,670)}You sure are standing out today as well
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.25,0:01:54.35,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(569.143,664.286)}Today's episode is produced by you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.57,0:02:00.40,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,She thought of various ways \Nto spook the other girls
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.40,0:02:01.97,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Unveil them, if you please
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.37,0:02:05.92,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\pos(537.143,666.571)}Here's what I've come up with for this episode
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.92,0:02:07.40,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It's quite packed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.07,0:02:10.22,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\i1}First set-up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.22,0:02:14.30,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(539.429,668.857)}Flashing a ghost photo on the studio monitor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.30,0:02:16.90,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(632,670)}Aah... That's a classic one
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:23.20,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(588.571,666.571)}We're trying to make it seem like \Nthis studio is haunted today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.35,0:02:25.40,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Second set-up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.40,0:02:27.85,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(625.143,670)}A girl's voice can suddenly be heard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:30.05,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,This is a really scary one
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.05,0:02:31.55,Marin,,0,0,0,,Super scary
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.55,0:02:38.92,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\pos(484.572,674.572)}Even during recording, when the manager suddenly play something through our headphone...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.92,0:02:40.37,Marin,,0,0,0,,everyone would scream
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.57,0:02:42.55,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(589.714,668.857)}Hopefully they'll do so in front of camera
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:43.45,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\pos(590.857,624.286)}Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:44.92,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Third set-up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.20,0:02:50.75,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(497.143,671.143)}The light flickers when Hidaka says something like "My head hurts from pushing myself too hard."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:52.05,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I see, I see
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.05,0:02:56.90,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(522.286,667.714)}You'll be doing this throughout the show, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.80,0:02:56.90,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\pos(526.857,625.429)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:02:58.57,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,As many times as you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:02:59.20,Marin,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:00.62,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Just say {\i1}"My head hurts."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.62,0:03:01.80,Marin,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:03.02,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fourth set-up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:07.87,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(602.286,668.857)}When Hidaka says "My shoulder hurts", Mori-sensei will feel a back pain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.15,0:03:11.95,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Do I shout it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.95,0:03:16.75,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It's so painful that it'll make me \Nshout "OUCH!" all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:18.20,Marin,,0,0,0,,Make it subtle
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:19.70,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,This will be hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:22.92,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It'll be hard but I'll try
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.92,0:03:24.32,Marin,,0,0,0,,I'll leave it to you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:25.85,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fifth set-up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:30.07,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\pos(596.571,670)\i1}When Mori-sensei claps his hands, \NHidaka will do some mysterious action{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.07,0:03:32.15,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I'll be the trigger for this one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:33.07,Marin,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.07,0:03:35.65,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if I can do it naturally
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.15,0:03:37.95,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What is this mysterious action?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.95,0:03:39.72,Marin,,0,0,0,,For example...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.47,0:03:46.52,Marin,,0,0,0,,Or acting like I had been \Npossessed by something
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:49.05,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Don't get exposed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:53.12,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(515.429,672.286)}We also prepared our best prank right at the end
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:56.55,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(568,665.428)}so just enjoy the show without worries
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.82,0:03:59.27,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,The actual show is about to start
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.27,0:04:01.90,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Everyone must've thought \Nthere was a technical problem
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.95,0:04:05.70,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Well then, please enjoy the show~
