Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.71,0:26:24.61,Topics (Thin Outline),,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\3c&H475E2D&\fscx90\fscy93\3a&H00&\pos(673.144,676.858)}in the dead of night when people are sound asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.85,0:22:51.82,Kano,,0,0,0,,What was it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.82,0:22:53.87,Marin,,0,0,0,,I've heard of it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.60,0:22:53.82,Kano,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.12,0:22:56.80,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,This is probably the hardest question
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.80,0:23:00.82,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Even I couldn't think of the answer right away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.72,0:23:04.50,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It may be difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.50,0:23:13.20,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Well, it's a term that sometimes comes up in the ghost story that children reads
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.02,0:23:17.20,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Hint, it's made up of four kanji characters
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.95,0:23:18.50,Kano,,0,0,0,,No way
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.97,0:23:19.77,Kano,,0,0,0,,Mine's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.50,0:23:22.25,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Hidaka doesn't seem like she could only write four kanji
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.82,0:23:24.32,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You got this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.32,0:23:26.02,Kano,,0,0,0,,So it's made up of four kanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.02,0:23:29.47,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,There's a possibility that it's not as well. Believe in yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.77,0:23:32.25,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You've already wrote your answer after all
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.37,0:23:36.37,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What is the parade called?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.15,0:23:40.05,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.67,0:23:43.52,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Do your best everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.67,0:23:45.00,T/N,,0,0,0,,[T/N: Poor Mori-sensei. Marin didn't pick up the cue. lol]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.02,0:23:45.00,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.25,0:23:47.85,Marin,,0,0,0,,You can move just fine
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.37,0:23:50.65,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.65,0:23:54.32,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It's extremely painful if I bend my back this way
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.70,0:23:56.97,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.75,0:24:02.55,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What do you call the Yokai parade that begins in the dead of night when people are sound asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.55,0:24:03.77,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Wanna have a go, Fujihira?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.77,0:24:04.30,Kano,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.30,0:24:05.90,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Show your answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.05,0:24:07.10,Kano,,0,0,0,,Sleep paralysis
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.42,0:24:08.67,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Sleep paralysis huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.90,0:24:12.90,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,So they're doing the parade while also making you unable to move huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.62,0:24:16.25,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,That's a rather interesting drawing
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.37,0:24:19.00,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,How are the others doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.32,0:24:20.70,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Anyone done?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.02,0:24:23.52,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.52,0:24:25.90,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Think harder Hidaka
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.27,0:24:29.22,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You seem knowledgeable in this matter
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.22,0:24:30.22,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I don't know the kanji
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.50,0:24:32.82,Kokona,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's what
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.10,0:24:37.35,Marin,,0,0,0,,Ehh? Gimme a sec
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.85,0:24:38.57,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Ohh!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.90,0:24:43.10,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Nonaka has once again included a drawing. \NLet's have a look at it
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.55,0:24:44.42,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Done?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.45,0:24:45.20,Kokona,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.20,0:24:47.32,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Let's see it! Show them!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.15,0:24:51.30,Kokona,,0,0,0,,Jinyokoushin (lit: PeopleNightParade)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.42,0:24:54.82,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It does sound like it could be that
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.82,0:24:55.80,Kano,,0,0,0,,Exactly as it is
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.80,0:25:00.60,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,The Yokai parade that begins in the dead of night when people are asleep, or in short, PeopleNightParade huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.00,0:25:04.12,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You just cut most of the words out!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.62,0:25:07.05,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Don't you laugh at it, sleep paralysis girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.75,0:25:10.40,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Are you done, Shintani?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.40,0:25:11.97,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Alright, show them!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.70,0:25:15.45,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Reigun Mikkai (lit: SpiritArmySecretMeeting)
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.62,0:25:17.67,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,That seems likely!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.87,0:25:19.50,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.50,0:25:22.00,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Sounds possible, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.00,0:25:27.62,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It was hit or miss but it's still a very educated guess
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.12,0:25:24.97,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.27,0:25:29.87,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Sounds possible... Maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.45,0:25:32.77,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Finalize yours too, Hidaka
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.45,0:25:37.80,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What have you been looking at??
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.80,0:25:38.70,Marin,,0,0,0,,Nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.87,0:25:40.00,Kano,,0,0,0,,That's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.80,0:25:42.92,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I'm scared for my back
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.92,0:25:44.35,Kano,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Super scary
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.07,0:25:44.85,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.85,0:25:48.72,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Even in dorms, I'm scared for my back so I'm always leaning against the wall
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.95,0:25:47.50,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.90,0:25:50.10,Kano,,0,0,0,,The mirror is scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.10,0:25:52.37,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Afraid that something could be behind you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.47,0:25:53.42,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,That's why I'd touch my back
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.42,0:25:54.37,Kano,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.37,0:25:55.42,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What do you mean??
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.25,0:25:58.17,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,Like this! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.42,0:26:01.02,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,So, if {\i1}"something"{\i0}  were to hug you-
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.50,0:26:04.00,Kano,,0,0,0,,Please stop! For real!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.00,0:26:07.12,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I wasn't even trying to scare you at all just now
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.12,0:26:10.17,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Well, let's take a look at Hidaka's answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.65,0:26:14.22,Marin,,0,0,0,,Hidamashii Youyuku (lit: FlamingSpiritsMovement)
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.87,0:26:16.17,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,The heck is that!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.17,0:26:19.25,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,FlamingSpiritsMovement participated by Yokai
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.72,0:26:22.37,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Well, it's something like that
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.52,0:26:24.37,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Here's the correct answer!
Comment: 0,0:26:24.61,0:26:40.77,Topics,,0,0,0,,Quiz 4 Answer
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.61,0:26:40.77,Topics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\3c&H475E2D&\c&H1010E8&\fscx115\fscy180\3a&H00&\pos(640,644.572)}Answer: Hyakki Yakou (Night Parade of 100 Demons)
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.75,0:26:26.90,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It's Hyakki Yakou
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.90,0:26:29.37,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,I didn't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.67,0:26:29.37,Marin,,0,0,0,,I've heard of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.50,0:26:34.55,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,If you don't remember this, they'll come for you
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.87,0:26:32.32,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Huh??
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.35,0:26:35.52,Marin,,0,0,0,,I have to make a note
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.52,0:26:38.35,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,But you can't take this back home!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.35,0:26:39.70,Marin,,0,0,0,,I'll tear the notes off
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.70,0:26:43.12,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Anyway, since everyone has 20 points,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.12,0:26:45.00,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It's a draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.10,0:26:49.85,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,The only thing that you guys knew were Rokurokubi
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.97,0:26:51.25,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Is it over already?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.02,0:26:52.05,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.65,0:26:55.05,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,The final result is a draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.65,0:26:58.22,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,That's the end of the first period!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.60,0:27:01.65,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Enjoy the break time everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.65,0:27:02.52,Marin,,0,0,0,,Okay
