Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.10,0:27:11.32,Kano,,0,0,0,,Time to read... the postcards!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.10,0:27:12.90,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.90,0:27:13.92,Kano,,0,0,0,,All yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.92,0:27:14.87,Marin,,0,0,0,,Shall I?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.65,0:27:17.25,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Sure, go ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.25,0:27:20.17,Marin,,0,0,0,,Such a wonderful mountain
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.17,0:27:21.57,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Oh wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.57,0:27:23.65,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,How wonderful~
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.40,0:27:25.72,Marin,,0,0,0,,I'll read 'em now
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.72,0:27:26.62,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Wonderful!
