Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.70,0:28:07.30,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Although it's still hot, please do your best during lesson!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.70,0:28:08.97,Marin,,0,0,0,,From Asariba
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.17,0:28:11.67,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.35,0:28:14.15,Kano,,0,0,0,,Kano wants to go to Hokkaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.35,0:28:15.97,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Yeah, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.97,0:28:17.80,Kano,,0,0,0,,I wanna go to Hokkaido
