Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.90,0:28:19.60,Marin,,0,0,0,,Same!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.60,0:28:21.02,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,It's vast
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.25,0:28:22.40,Marin,,0,0,0,,I wanna eat the Hotate (scallop) there
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.52,0:28:23.42,Kokona,,0,0,0,,Me too
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.42,0:28:25.47,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Who here has climbed a mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.47,0:28:26.22,Marin,,0,0,0,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.42,0:28:27.82,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.02,0:28:32.72,Marin,,0,0,0,,We went mountain climbing for training camp every year in my elementary school
