Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.57,0:29:09.90,Marin,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's true that the climbing is a struggle
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.90,0:29:14.95,Marin,,0,0,0,,but the moment you reached the top and see this scenery
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.37,0:29:14.95,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I wanna see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.27,0:29:19.32,Marin,,0,0,0,,it makes you want to climb the mountain all over again
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.32,0:29:21.07,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,You won't understand unless you climb huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.07,0:29:21.90,Marin,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.07,0:29:23.35,Kano,,0,0,0,,I wanna climb!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.35,0:29:25.70,Marin,,0,0,0,,It feels like you're on top of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.70,0:29:27.07,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,That's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.40,0:29:29.20,Marin,,0,0,0,,Wonderful
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.20,0:29:33.00,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to hear that they listen to Sakura Gakuin songs on top of the mountain
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.00,0:29:34.65,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,I know right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.65,0:29:36.87,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.17,0:29:39.72,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Let's read one more
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.72,0:29:40.77,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.77,0:29:41.82,Kano,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.62,0:29:47.70,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Good evening to everyone in Sakura Gakuin, \NMori-sensei and the staff!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.82,0:29:49.07,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.27,0:29:52.42,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Thank you for making my Monday awesome every week!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.75,0:29:56.22,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Well then! This week's theme is summer break."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.32,0:30:02.22,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I don't really have any summer break but I go surfing in summer every year."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.65,0:30:03.32,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.32,0:30:08.92,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"It's also one of the events in Tokyo Olympics so I'll be glad if you'll keep an eye on it."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.37,0:30:12.72,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Are there any marine sports that you want to try out?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.05,0:30:15.47,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Enjoy the last summer of Heisei period!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.67,0:30:16.70,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,From Toki-san
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.70,0:30:19.05,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.82,0:30:19.40,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,"It's Aritomo-san!" written here
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.47,0:30:22.35,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,Aritomo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.25,0:30:22.40,Kano,,0,0,0,,Ohh wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.67,0:30:24.35,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,Kawaii!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.35,0:30:26.32,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm not Aritomoto
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.77,0:30:28.25,Marin,,0,0,0,,Marine sports huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.25,0:30:30.35,Kano,,0,0,0,,Kano wants to go surfing
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.35,0:30:31.02,Marin,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.20,0:30:33.57,Kano,,0,0,0,,Don't you wanna try it even though it seems hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.57,0:30:35.67,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I wanna try riding on a banana boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.32,0:30:38.62,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Sounds fun, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.62,0:30:39.82,Marin,,0,0,0,,We'll definitely fall
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.82,0:30:41.52,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Right? We'll lose balance
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.52,0:30:46.20,Marin,,0,0,0,,I wanna try out the water jetpack that makes you fly
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.20,0:30:47.77,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,The one that makes you hover?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.77,0:30:50.92,Kano,,0,0,0,,I want! Good balancing skill seems essential for it though
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.25,0:30:52.75,Kokona,,0,0,0,,I wanna go surfing
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.95,0:30:56.35,Kano,,0,0,0,,I know right! Same with me
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.37,0:30:57.60,Marin,,0,0,0,,Ride the wave
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.60,0:30:59.37,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Right? I wanna go to the beach
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.07,0:31:01.52,Kano,,0,0,0,,I wanna go with everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.52,0:31:02.47,Kokona,,0,0,0,,Everyone in SG
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.47,0:31:06.82,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Let's work even harder and then request the teacher to let us go there
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.82,0:31:07.72,Kano,,0,0,0,,Request!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.72,0:31:09.00,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,"We wanna go to the beach!"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.82,0:31:09.57,Kano,,0,0,0,,Please~
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.37,0:31:13.82,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Thank you Toki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.75,0:31:17.15,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,So many dreams for summer break
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.62,0:31:20.42,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,And yet they always end up unfulfilled though
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.42,0:31:26.92,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Now that you're the president, you should take command and organize a strike or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.10,0:31:32.05,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Be like "We won't practice unless you fulfill them!"
Dialogue: 1,0:31:32.32,0:31:34.37,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Alright! Moving on to the second period!
Comment: 0,0:31:34.31,0:31:39.37,Topics,,0,0,0,,Second Period
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.31,0:31:39.37,Topics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fscx120\fscy160\pos(662.476,688.571)}FRESH{\i1}!{\i0} Monday, Ghost Storytelling in Midsummer {\i1}!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.77,0:31:39.85,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,599.143)}FRESH! Monday, Ghost Storytelling in Midsummer!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.05,0:31:42.15,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,This is where we get down to today's main topic!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.27,0:31:44.47,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You'll be reading some ghost stories
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.47,0:31:48.47,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Being skillful at this is also crucial to becoming a Super Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.47,0:31:53.67,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,So do your best to frighten the viewers with your storytelling
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.87,0:31:58.10,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,For this, you'll be in a group of two
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.82,0:32:01.20,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,and read your story together
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.20,0:32:09.25,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Both groups are clueless about the other's story so there's a possibility that you'd be scared by it as well
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.25,0:32:11.85,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,How will the team be divided?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.75,0:32:14.97,Kokona,,0,0,0,,Marin-chan and me
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.75,0:32:14.97,Marin,,0,0,0,,Kokona and me
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.97,0:32:18.52,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,So Nonaka and Hidaka, \Nand Shintani and Fujihira
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.67,0:32:20.30,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Are you two gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.30,0:32:24.27,Kano,,0,0,0,,No, we won't! We're always scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.27,0:32:26.60,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You even get scared from reading it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.17,0:32:27.67,Kano,,0,0,0,,Really scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.67,0:32:29.17,Marin,,0,0,0,,There's candle now...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.17,0:32:31.15,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Why? Something wrong with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.90,0:32:33.15,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Are you scared, Hidaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.15,0:32:34.40,Marin,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.82,0:32:36.35,Marin,,0,0,0,,I'm not feeling well today
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.35,0:32:39.60,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,The fact that Marin is not feeling well is scary
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.60,0:32:40.92,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,That's a sign, you know
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.37,0:32:42.92,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,The heck is happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.92,0:32:45.17,Kano,,0,0,0,,I really hate this! I can't! I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.45,0:32:48.97,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Was that a pr- \NOh well, whatever. Let's move on
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.32,0:32:52.95,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Let's see... Who'll go first?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.95,0:32:58.27,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I guess we'll start with team Hidaka and Nonaka first
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.50,0:33:00.05,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Ready... Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.50,0:33:03.27,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Wait! Will it stay like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.27,0:33:04.30,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I guess so
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.30,0:33:05.50,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Isn't it too dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.92,0:33:07.05,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Okay, nevermind
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.42,0:33:12.17,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It's your groan that's scary
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.85,0:33:14.10,Kano,,0,0,0,,Let's move over there a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.65,0:33:13.32,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.92,0:33:17.50,Kano,,0,0,0,,Wait, Kano doesn't like the gap here
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.15,0:33:18.27,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I'll follow
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.75,0:33:19.90,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.10,0:33:21.57,Marin,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.62,0:33:22.82,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Go ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.82,0:33:23.55,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.17,0:33:25.45,Marin,,0,0,0,,"Present"
Comment: 0,0:33:26.74,0:39:18.41,Topics,,0,0,0,,Second Period, First Story
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.74,0:39:18.41,Topics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&H7F11DE&\3c&HECEBEC&\3a&H0E&\fscx140\fscy116\bord60\clip(m 965 630 l 965 629 966 628 966 631 b 964 626 971 617 980 620 l 1237 620 b 1244 619 1250 624 1250 631 l 1250 680 b 1251 688 1246 692 1240 694 l 979 694 b 972 695 965 692 964 682)\pos(1110.286,685.143)}PRESENT
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.80,0:33:30.22,Marin,,0,0,0,,This is a true story
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.85,0:33:35.72,Marin,,0,0,0,,Eiko-san who is an office worker at a neighbouring company
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.87,0:33:41.50,Marin,,0,0,0,,has been harassed by a stalker since around a week ago
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.77,0:33:46.02,Marin,,0,0,0,,As for the harassment...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.65,0:33:52.52,Marin,,0,0,0,,She finds weird things inside her mail box every morning
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.77,0:33:56.30,Marin,,0,0,0,,First, a shoelace
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.35,0:33:59.87,Marin,,0,0,0,,Next, a belt buckle
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.97,0:34:02.60,Marin,,0,0,0,,The next one is...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.07,0:34:05.52,Marin,,0,0,0,,a shirt button
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.65,0:34:09.50,Marin,,0,0,0,,Then, on the next day, there was a beanie inside it
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.70,0:34:15.47,Kokona,,0,0,0,,However, because there hasn't been anything else since then,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.72,0:34:21.05,Kokona,,0,0,0,,EIko-san didn't inform the police despite feeling eerie about it
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.85,0:34:24.95,Kokona,,0,0,0,,On a morning a few days after the last incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.70,0:34:30.52,Kokona,,0,0,0,,while thinking {\i1}"What on earth was all those about anyway"{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.97,0:34:34.90,Kokona,,0,0,0,,Eiko-san went to her mail box to pick up the newspaper
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.02,0:34:41.75,Kokona,,0,0,0,,As she opened her mail box, she found a letter instead of a newspaper
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.62,0:34:44.52,Kokona,,0,0,0,,The content are as follows
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.72,0:34:48.47,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Sorry to have kept you waiting for so long."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.55,0:34:54.12,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I gave you presents that represent my feelings starting from my feet."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.82,0:34:57.25,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"But, before long, I reached my head already."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.25,0:35:00.22,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I thought about what I should do next."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.52,0:35:04.60,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"A good idea came to me though it took me quite awhile."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.65,0:35:09.55,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Look forward to it from tomorrow onwards."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.90,0:35:13.67,Kokona,,0,0,0,,Eiko-san immediately dropped to the floor in terror
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.20,0:35:18.95,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"It must be him..."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.90,0:35:25.80,Kokona,,0,0,0,,Eiko-san was scared to stay at home that day so she stayed overnight at a friend's house
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.52,0:35:32.40,Kokona,,0,0,0,,On the next morning, Eiko-san went back to her home for a change of clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.00,0:35:36.75,Kokona,,0,0,0,,She wondered about what might be inside her mail box
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.75,0:35:41.52,Kokona,,0,0,0,,Despite the fear, she opened it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.67,0:35:45.10,Marin,,0,0,0,,What she found inside was...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.10,0:35:47.60,Marin,,0,0,0,,a bloodied toenail
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.35,0:35:54.77,Marin,,0,0,0,,Next to it was another letter
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.02,0:35:59.25,Marin,,0,0,0,,The letter reads as follows
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.60,0:36:05.17,Kokona,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"After my clothes, I'll now be giving you parts of my body from the bottom up."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.90,0:36:09.85,Kokona,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Oh! But it would be bad if you stay at your friend's house."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.15,0:36:13.00,Kokona,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Cause I like visiting you when you're sleeping at home."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.67,0:36:18.47,Kokona,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"If you sleep at your friend's house again, I might do the same things to her."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.60,0:36:22.12,Kokona,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Telling the police won't change a thing as well"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.75,0:36:25.35,Kokona,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Look forward to tomorrow as well, okay?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.65,0:36:30.97,Marin,,0,0,0,,Eiko-san trembled in fear and felt completely helpless
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.07,0:36:33.92,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I can't escape him anymore"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.35,0:36:37.60,Marin,,0,0,0,,Eiko-san took a leave from work
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.92,0:36:41.50,Marin,,0,0,0,,and shut herself in her home for hours on end
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.35,0:36:49.52,Marin,,0,0,0,,Unable to sleep... All she did was tremble in fear at the corner of her room
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.10,0:36:56.42,Marin,,0,0,0,,And of course, she couldn't check her mail box
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.17,0:37:02.45,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Then, on a morning several days later, her front door bell rang
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.27,0:37:15.02,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I've been on leave for days so it could be someone from work who's worried about me."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.95,0:37:17.80,Marin,,0,0,0,,Thinking that...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.25,0:37:22.52,Marin,,0,0,0,,She went to open the door
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.52,0:37:24.75,Marin,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.65,0:37:27.60,Marin,,0,0,0,,There was no one outside
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.87,0:37:34.05,Marin,,0,0,0,,Then, as she was about to close the door
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.37,0:37:38.12,Marin,,0,0,0,,The things that caught her eyes were
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.12,0:37:42.32,Marin,,0,0,0,,Fingernails scattered on the ground...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.77,0:37:44.12,Marin,,0,0,0,,Hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.67,0:37:45.95,Marin,,0,0,0,,And lastly...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.67,0:37:48.15,Marin,,0,0,0,,Eyeballs
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.77,0:38:05.15,Marin,,0,0,0,,Eiko-san's phone rang
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.37,0:38:09.07,Marin,,0,0,0,,She fearfully answered it
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.55,0:38:13.57,Kokona,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Why didn't you accept my presents?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.35,0:38:18.32,Kokona,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I prepared lots of them for you, \Nand yet, you accepted none."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.62,0:38:23.40,Kokona,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Ohh I see! You're already satisfied with all the presents, right?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.87,0:38:26.77,Kokona,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"If so, why don't you give me your presents then?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.85,0:38:29.50,Marin,,0,0,0,,Eiko-san threw away the phone
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.50,0:38:32.70,Marin,,0,0,0,,and ran outside barefooted
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.00,0:38:40.50,Marin,,0,0,0,,However, Eiko-san became exhausted after not eating for days since leaving her home
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.02,0:38:44.32,Marin,,0,0,0,,She became unable to move right then and there
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.65,0:38:48.15,Kokona,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"What kind of present will you give me?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.20,0:38:56.75,Marin,,0,0,0,,She turned around and a bloodied man who is without his hair, fingernails and both his eyes was standing there
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.72,0:39:03.97,Kokona,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Since I gave you that many presents, it's fine if I ask you to give me what I want, right?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.37,0:39:06.35,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\fs80\}KYAAAAAAAAAAHHH!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.92,0:39:06.35,Kano,,0,0,0,,{\fs80\}KYAAAAAAAAAAHHH!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.92,0:39:16.55,Kokona,,0,0,0,,After that, Eiko-san's whereabouts became \Nunknown and she remains missing to this day
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.35,0:39:32.00,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Wait... Can you zoom in on Shintani-san's face?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.95,0:39:36.60,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.80,0:39:40.87,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What... What kind of expression is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.05,0:39:43.45,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You were the most frightened
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.17,0:39:46.45,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.45,0:39:48.65,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It was really good, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.05,0:39:53.40,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,This is a segment where you try to scare others after all
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.67,0:39:56.92,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Seriously, what's wrong with you Shintani??
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.92,0:39:59.50,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Please say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.75,0:40:02.92,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,She only screamed because it's written there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.32,0:40:06.57,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,{\fs120\bord10}I CAN'T STAND THIS!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.72,0:40:09.17,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.35,0:40:12.72,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.72,0:40:17.60,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I'm not really frightened by this. \NIt's the dorm that I'm scared of
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.60,0:40:18.47,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Dorm??
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.47,0:40:19.15,Kano,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.15,0:40:24.32,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,What should I do if that person comes to our dorm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.32,0:40:27.52,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! You're well-protected
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.95,0:40:29.47,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,He won't come to your dorm
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.47,0:40:30.32,Kano,,0,0,0,,He will, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.32,0:40:32.85,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,She said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.05,0:40:34.85,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Hidaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.40,0:40:36.15,Kano,,0,0,0,,Hey now!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.80,0:40:38.02,Marin,,0,0,0,,I'm fine
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.17,0:40:39.10,Marin,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.62,0:40:41.02,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Well then!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.17,0:40:45.07,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Nonaka was great just now, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.40,0:40:47.07,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Her expression for example
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.07,0:40:48.87,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with Hidaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.05,0:40:53.40,Kano,,0,0,0,,Hidaka was talking the whole time in the dressing room
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.35,0:40:52.07,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.40,0:40:55.20,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Who was she talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.42,0:40:57.10,Marin,,0,0,0,,She's talking to herself
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.47,0:41:02.50,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Can you stop acting so scary? \NWe'll honestly get scared if you continue
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.50,0:41:03.20,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Seriously
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.20,0:41:05.65,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You're doing it to the wrong bunch
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.82,0:41:06.27,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.27,0:41:11.20,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Next up! It's Shintani's and Fujihira's turn
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.52,0:41:12.85,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine, we're just reading them. It's not scary at all
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.25,0:41:12.47,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,That's true
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.85,0:41:16.17,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,That scream just now was so unexpected, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.17,0:41:18.15,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,That's the scariest part!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.15,0:41:19.57,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,The story wasn't as scary
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.57,0:41:21.70,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It's the scream that gets you
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.07,0:41:24.82,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Did you improvise that or was it written?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.82,0:41:25.87,Marin,,0,0,0,,It's written
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.87,0:41:29.07,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You deserve a perfect mark for reenacting the scream
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.77,0:41:29.57,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.57,0:41:31.95,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It's frustrating but you have to agree
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.80,0:41:31.95,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Yes... Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.95,0:41:33.70,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Amusing!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.70,0:41:36.10,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You're really amusing, Shintani!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.90,0:41:40.40,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Even us got scared after reading the story
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.40,0:41:42.37,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,The story choice is a bit too scary
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.37,0:41:44.95,Kano,,0,0,0,,I'm always called for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.22,0:41:46.40,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.07,0:41:48.40,Kano,,0,0,0,,Always!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.40,0:41:49.40,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I wonder why
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.40,0:41:50.52,Kano,,0,0,0,,Always!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.87,0:41:52.85,Kano,,0,0,0,,Every single time!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.87,0:41:52.85,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Now then!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.95,0:41:56.40,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Here's Shintani and Fujihira reading their ghost story
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.50,0:41:57.45,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.70,0:42:08.97,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,At a certain junior high school, there was a ghost story that had been circulating since long time ago
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.60,0:42:14.47,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,It was rumored that if you go to the music room at night,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.47,0:42:19.62,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,the ghost of a woman who committed suicide will appear
Dialogue: 1,0:42:20.90,0:42:29.40,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,This is a story of Eiko-san, a student who went to that school and had actually experienced it
Comment: 0,0:42:24.94,0:47:15.64,Topics,,0,0,0,,Second Period, Second Story
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.94,0:47:15.64,Topics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&H7F11DE&\3c&HECEBEC&\3a&H0C&\fscx65\fscy100\bord60\clip(m 966 633 b 966 624 972 617 981 620 l 1238 620 b 1243 620 1251 623 1250 632 l 1250 681 b 1249 688 1245 695 1239 694 l 981 694 b 973 697 965 690 966 682)\pos(1109.714,681.142)}Music Room at Night
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.65,0:42:35.30,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,It happened in the middle of the final exam period of the second semester
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.72,0:42:41.42,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Eiko-san was doing some last minute cramming for the exam
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.42,0:42:44.97,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,When the night comes, she realizes something
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.27,0:42:48.62,Kano,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"There's an exam tomorrow."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.30,0:42:54.87,Kano,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"But I don't have my Science textbook with me. I'd fail my paper at this rate."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.45,0:43:01.55,Kano,,0,0,0,,And so, she decided to go to the school at night to get her textbook back
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.40,0:43:06.50,Kano,,0,0,0,,She arrived at the school's guard post
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.05,0:43:10.12,Kano,,0,0,0,,However, there was no one there
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.72,0:43:14.30,Kano,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I'll run out of time to study if I don't hurry!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.52,0:43:20.47,Kano,,0,0,0,,Thinking that, she decided to sneak into the school
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.50,0:43:26.27,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Eiko-san walked cautiously through the dark hallway
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.32,0:43:35.67,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Despite the eerie feeling in the air, she climbed the stairs and found her way to her classroom
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.37,0:43:44.25,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,She went inside and found her textbook in her locker
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.20,0:43:48.75,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Phew! Thank god!"
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.62,0:43:52.40,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I have to hurry back home and study."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.70,0:44:01.30,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Just as Eiko-san was leaving the classrom while saying that, something happened
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.00,0:44:08.97,Kano,,0,0,0,,She could hear the sound of piano coming from the music room
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.52,0:44:12.42,Kano,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Who could it be, this late at night?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.90,0:44:18.40,Kano,,0,0,0,,Eiko-san became curious and couldn't hold herself back
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.85,0:44:23.05,Kano,,0,0,0,,She made her way to the music room one step at a time
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.42,0:44:31.57,Kano,,0,0,0,,As she gets closer to the music room, the piano sound steadily gets louder
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.62,0:44:29.87,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(888,324.857)}Whatchu want??
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.32,0:44:35.02,Kano,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"There must be someone there!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.77,0:44:41.22,Kano,,0,0,0,,She plucked up her courage and opened the door
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.35,0:44:47.25,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,However, there was no one inside
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.00,0:44:51.00,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,The piano sound disappeared as well
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.17,0:44:58.90,Kano,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I must've misheard it due to the lack of sleep from all the cramming."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.27,0:45:04.02,Kano,,0,0,0,,She told herself that and left the room
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.82,0:45:07.80,Kano,,0,0,0,,However, as soon as she closed the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.20,0:45:14.22,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,She could hear the piano being played again
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.75,0:45:18.67,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,"Someone's making fun of me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.60,0:45:24.32,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,She hurried back to the music room
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.45,0:45:32.52,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,She then looked in front of the piano and \Naround it but there was no one to be found
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.60,0:45:36.30,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,The keylid was closed as well
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.62,0:45:42.10,Kano,,0,0,0,,Unable to comprehend what's happening, \NEiko-san opened the keylid and tried playing them
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.00,0:45:44.80,Kano,,0,0,0,,However, it didn't make any sound
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.85,0:45:50.37,Kano,,0,0,0,,No sound were made no matter how hard she pressed the key
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.35,0:45:55.62,Kano,,0,0,0,,Then, the moment Eiko-san pressed \Nthe keys with both her hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.02,0:45:58.02,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,{\fs80}KYAAAAAHHHHH!!!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.45,0:46:03.02,Kano,,0,0,0,,Her hands were caught in between the lid and the keys
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.92,0:46:07.30,Kano,,0,0,0,,Blood trickled down from her hands
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.12,0:46:13.10,Kano,,0,0,0,,Unable to move, Eiko-san screamed until she lost her voice
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.30,0:46:19.65,Kano,,0,0,0,,The music room became dead silent
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.10,0:46:25.97,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Then, she heard a voice coming from behind her
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.60,0:46:31.30,Kano,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"What are you doing with my piano?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.17,0:46:35.17,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,She nervously turned her head around
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.72,0:46:39.02,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,and there was a woman smeared with blood
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.45,0:46:42.70,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Eiko-san was silenced by fear
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.67,0:46:48.25,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Then, the bloodied woman said this to her
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.32,0:46:56.10,Kano,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Since you played my precious piano without my permission, I guess you don't need those fingers anymore, do you?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.67,0:47:04.75,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Eiko-san was absent from school on the next day
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.00,0:47:07.87,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,The next day...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.87,0:47:09.87,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,And the days that follows...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.35,0:47:14.17,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,She never turned up to school
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.22,0:47:19.12,Kano,,0,0,0,,Scary
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.30,0:47:23.55,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,There we have it
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.42,0:47:26.32,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Umm... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.32,0:47:28.82,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Shintani's scream fell flat though
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.37,0:47:34.40,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You wanted to return the favor but they didn't really fell for it
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.12,0:47:36.15,Kano,,0,0,0,,Wait a sec
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.95,0:47:38.10,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,At such a crucial part-
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.10,0:47:41.27,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's first go back to our usual setup
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.50,0:47:42.95,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,With lights and all
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.65,0:47:44.82,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Now then
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.27,0:47:48.40,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Shall we move forward for now?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.47,0:47:50.57,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Alright
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.47,0:47:55.72,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Let's hear your thoughts about this segment
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.52,0:47:58.32,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Come forward
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.77,0:47:59.50,Kano,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.50,0:48:01.45,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I'm scared of Hidaka more than anything
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.45,0:48:02.00,Kano,,0,0,0,,Ehh??
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.00,0:48:03.27,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Ehh?? What??
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.32,0:48:07.42,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Let's umm... Let's just line up in the middle first
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.72,0:48:13.47,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the ghost story lesson...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.47,0:48:14.37,Kano,,0,0,0,,She okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.85,0:48:16.65,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Umm... Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.40,0:48:19.87,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Well uhh.. Alright, understood
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.40,0:48:24.90,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What's your thoughts about this, Nonaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.90,0:48:25.67,Kokona,,0,0,0,,Scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.67,0:48:27.30,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It really was scary
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.85,0:48:30.25,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Which part scared you?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.25,0:48:34.62,Kokona,,0,0,0,,I was still fine during the quiz but the talking alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.62,0:48:37.70,Kokona,,0,0,0,,\NOh! Yuzumi-chan's scream was scary
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.70,0:48:39.05,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Really? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.82,0:48:39.47,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,So that scared you after all
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.95,0:48:42.55,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Why are you looking glad after hearing just that?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.55,0:48:43.82,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Really? I'm so glad
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.82,0:48:46.32,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,But yeah, both teams were great
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.32,0:48:50.52,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Did you see Nonaka's expression just now? I guess you didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.12,0:48:51.00,Kano,,0,0,0,,I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.65,0:48:53.77,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You were clinging to each other the whole time
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.77,0:48:57.00,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Fujihira kept looking behind while reading
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.72,0:48:57.70,Kano,,0,0,0,,I was really scared
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.70,0:48:59.20,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It really was scary
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.67,0:49:02.47,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,How about you, Shintani?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.12,0:49:03.92,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.92,0:49:04.85,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.05,0:49:07.00,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Which part was scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.00,0:49:12.12,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,It's not the story, but rather the thought of it happening in real life that's scary
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.97,0:49:12.12,Kano,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, yes
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.12,0:49:12.95,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I see, I see
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.95,0:49:15.17,Kano,,0,0,0,,Yeah, when we get back to our dorm...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.25,0:49:18.12,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Yes... Ahh! I won't be able to sleep today!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.12,0:49:21.25,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I see, since you'll be remembering all these
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.12,0:49:19.00,Kano,,0,0,0,,Absolutely!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.25,0:49:22.62,Kano,,0,0,0,,I absolutely cannot
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.70,0:49:23.52,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Today...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.35,0:49:26.47,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What? What? What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.87,0:49:28.00,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What's happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.92,0:49:31.77,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Comment: 0,0:49:31.77,0:49:31.90,Kano,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs20\pos(218,667)}(Don't mind me...\NJust hiding here){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.90,0:49:33.67,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Ehh?? What's this??
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.05,0:49:38.05,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.25,0:49:40.05,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Where have you been!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.07,0:49:43.62,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,The heck is this!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.37,0:49:46.12,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It's Sadako!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.37,0:49:48.00,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.27,0:49:50.45,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Sadako is here!!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.52,0:49:53.75,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I was worried about you Marin!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.70,0:49:56.67,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.92,0:50:01.12,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,No! It's not that I was scared! \NI was just worried about Marin!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.12,0:50:02.65,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You were here??
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.25,0:50:06.32,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I thought you were sick or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.50,0:50:08.30,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.82,0:50:11.07,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.07,0:50:13.55,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I wasn't scared! I was worried about Marin!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.55,0:50:15.47,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You were worried huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.47,0:50:16.37,Marin,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.37,0:50:17.60,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Shintani!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.60,0:50:22.52,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,She has been acting strange ever since we were in the dressing room! I was so worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.52,0:50:24.22,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,She got you worried huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.22,0:50:27.87,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,However... Tell them the truth Hidaka
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.87,0:50:29.57,Marin,,0,0,0,,It's all an act!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.57,0:50:30.57,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,All of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.47,0:50:38.77,Marin,,0,0,0,,I've been acting ever since we were in dressing room today
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.22,0:50:41.22,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,She was acting so strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.45,0:50:44.72,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Alright everyone, let's uhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.72,0:50:45.80,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Fujihira-san too
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.30,0:50:47.35,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You okay Shintani?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.35,0:50:49.07,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,No, I'm just worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.02,0:50:49.22,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,How kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.22,0:50:52.62,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You were worried more than you were scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.20,0:50:51.57,Marin,,0,0,0,,It's all fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.52,0:50:53.90,Marin,,0,0,0,,Nothing wrong with me
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.20,0:50:55.22,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I'm so relieved!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.22,0:51:00.07,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,This somehow turned out to be a disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.45,0:51:06.75,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Nonaka kept checking on Hidaka \Nwhenever she was acting strange
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.90,0:51:08.02,Kano,,0,0,0,,I was so scared
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.02,0:51:12.60,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Nonaka kept on comforting her the whole time she was looking distressed
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.65,0:51:17.45,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I really thought she was sick or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.45,0:51:21.72,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You must be thinking like \N{\i1}"Don't joke around while I'm reading my story!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.72,0:51:24.47,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"And yet, I had to keep on reading!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.22,0:51:28.95,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Actually, you know that we started 3 minutes late, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.10,0:51:30.65,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.65,0:51:31.77,Kano,,0,0,0,,Eh? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.90,0:51:33.85,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I HATE THIS!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.57,0:51:35.10,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Yes, those 3 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.15,0:51:35.97,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I HATE THIS!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.97,0:51:36.97,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I HATE YOU!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.57,0:51:38.75,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.70,0:51:42.10,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I'm glad! I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.97,0:51:42.77,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,While the staff was-
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.77,0:51:48.65,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,During the 3 minutes, a pre-recorded video of me and Hidaka
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.65,0:51:52.52,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,revealing this set-up was broadcasted
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.52,0:51:54.70,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Flashing a ghost photo on the studio monitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.15,0:51:55.47,Kokona,,0,0,0,,I saw it! I saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.67,0:51:57.70,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,A girl's voice can suddenly be heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.70,0:51:59.27,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Was this played?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.27,0:52:00.72,Kano,,0,0,0,,I didn't hear it
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.85,0:52:03.85,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,The light flickers when Hidaka says "My head hurts"
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.50,0:52:07.40,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I'm more worried about her head hurting!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.80,0:52:11.57,Kano,,0,0,0,,Since she kept saying that, it's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.40,0:52:11.57,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,She made you worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.27,0:52:14.30,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Her acting was too good then
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.80,0:52:14.90,Kano,,0,0,0,,Too good!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.25,0:52:21.10,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Fourth, when Hidaka says "My shoulder hurts", Mori-sensei will feel a back pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.55,0:52:23.12,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,That too?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.12,0:52:25.27,Marin,,0,0,0,,I forgot about this
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.62,0:52:29.65,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I kept my backpain acting going the whole time
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.65,0:52:32.05,Kano,,0,0,0,,So that's why!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.05,0:52:37.15,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I started off with saying that I have \Nbackpain just because of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.15,0:52:39.65,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I've been worried about you since before we started
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.65,0:52:41.07,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Man! You're so kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.07,0:52:42.72,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I was so worried!!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.72,0:52:44.00,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Sorry! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.55,0:52:46.00,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Sorry Shintani!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.22,0:52:49.82,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,As for the reason why we went with this line-up,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.82,0:52:53.87,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,the teachers chose based on who gets scared the most
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.17,0:52:57.30,Kano,,0,0,0,,Seriously! I'm always chosen for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.42,0:53:00.87,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,And it was decided that it'd be the three of you
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.67,0:53:06.82,Marin,,0,0,0,,The teachers asked me who among the members get scared the most
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.82,0:53:08.35,Marin,,0,0,0,,And I told them
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.35,0:53:11.50,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,So, it's Hidaka's choice of members, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.65,0:53:13.32,Marin,,0,0,0,,Yes! That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.57,0:53:14.87,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Fujihira is the main choice every time!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.05,0:53:16.02,Kano,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(Yeah...){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.02,0:53:19.60,Kano,,0,0,0,,It's always me that had to sit near the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.00,0:53:21.80,Kano,,0,0,0,,I really hate this!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.37,0:53:25.07,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect you to hide under this desk!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.25,0:53:29.67,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What a waste! We wanted to see your reaction too!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.12,0:53:32.32,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect Shintani to be this surprised
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.32,0:53:34.32,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Next, fifth set-up
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.57,0:53:37.70,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,When Mori-sensei claps his hands, \NHidaka will do some mysterious action
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.50,0:53:40.90,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I was continuously getting ignored
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.90,0:53:41.87,Marin,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.80,0:53:45.42,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Did you remember? \NI clapped so hard just now
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.77,0:53:46.92,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I didn't know
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.25,0:53:50.75,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I clapped unusually just now, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.75,0:53:52.07,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Didn't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.07,0:53:53.75,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,And yet, Hidaka didn't react!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.75,0:53:55.70,Marin,,0,0,0,,You didn't clap hard enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.70,0:53:57.87,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I was clapping really hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.02,0:54:00.55,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I also made it obvious like "Hidaka! {\i1}(Clap){\i0}"
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.55,0:54:08.02,Marin,,0,0,0,,I noticed your cue during the ghost story and did it.\NBut other than that, I didn't remember at all
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.02,0:54:09.12,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I see, I see
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.27,0:54:13.47,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,The one where a girl's voice can be heard, was it played during break time?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.50,0:54:15.65,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,They said it was
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.85,0:54:16.95,Kokona,,0,0,0,,I didn't hear it
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.95,0:54:18.17,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You didn't? That sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.82,0:54:20.95,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You wanted to show your reactions, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.10,0:54:25.75,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Surprisingly, you were quite calm. Were you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.85,0:54:28.92,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You won't be picked for this anymore, y'know!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.05,0:54:32.10,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,So which is it! Are you glad?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.42,0:54:33.27,Kokona,,0,0,0,,I am glad
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.27,0:54:35.32,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What is that you're glad about?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.42,0:54:37.92,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,But yeah... Oh! Let's move on to the announcements
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.92,0:54:41.10,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,We did a lot and went a bit overboard today
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.17,0:54:45.42,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Well, please do the announcements
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.87,0:54:47.37,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Announcements please!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.60,0:54:52.07,Kano,,0,0,0,,Next week, on August 20th,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.07,0:54:56.40,Kano,,0,0,0,,Sakura Gakuin's Ganbare!! FRESH! Monday will be a Maaya special!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.75,0:55:01.45,Marin,,0,0,0,,Solo!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.70,0:55:03.20,Kano,,0,0,0,,Do your best! Seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.20,0:55:04.97,Marin,,0,0,0,,It'll be a live broadcast too
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.97,0:55:07.40,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Today's episode was produced by Hidaka
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.40,0:55:08.47,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.47,0:55:09.75,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.75,0:55:10.77,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Oh wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.45,0:55:11.25,Kano,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.25,0:55:14.92,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Well of course, that's what we had been talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.10,0:55:16.95,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Why do you only realize it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.95,0:55:17.85,Kano,,0,0,0,,I get it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.85,0:55:20.67,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Next week will be handled by Asou alone
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.17,0:55:23.37,Marin,,0,0,0,,Send her lots of postcards!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.37,0:55:24.37,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,Please do!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.37,0:55:25.37,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Questions perhaps
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.37,0:55:26.65,Kano,,0,0,0,,Or Maaya-related
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.65,0:55:31.02,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It'll be like when I did my solo episode with a radio-like set-up
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.02,0:55:34.02,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Having those postcards will help to motivate her
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.72,0:55:36.07,Kano,,0,0,0,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.60,0:55:39.32,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Since she'll probably be really anxious about this
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.42,0:55:40.32,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,We'll be watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.32,0:55:41.90,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Do your best Asou!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.90,0:55:43.82,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Let's move on
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.82,0:55:44.82,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.32,0:55:48.95,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,On September 7th, "Manners Lesson" will be held!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.27,0:55:55.30,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Yesterday... I forgot her name
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.30,0:55:57.77,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You did, and what's worse is that she was there
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.27,0:56:00.20,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.20,0:56:03.65,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,We greeted her after the show...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.67,0:56:05.70,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Her name was written on a piece of paper here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.80,0:56:07.47,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,That's the worse manner!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.07,0:56:09.12,Kano,,0,0,0,,Honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.12,0:56:10.40,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I messed up
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.40,0:56:11.60,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I already remember it!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.12,0:56:15.05,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,The lecturer will be Sunai Emi-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.15,0:56:19.65,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,We still don't know what we'll be doing
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.65,0:56:21.92,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,But please look forward to it everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.92,0:56:24.95,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,Please do!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.95,0:56:26.02,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Is there more?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.17,0:56:31.70,Marin,,0,0,0,,On the same day as the Manners Lesson, this show, Ganbare!! FRESH! Monday...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.35,0:56:37.20,Marin,,0,0,0,,will be broadcasting a pre-recorded video at 9 pm
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.75,0:56:42.35,Marin,,0,0,0,,Be sure to watch this too after you finish watching the Manners Lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.35,0:56:44.30,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,Please do!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.27,0:56:44.70,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,How thoughtful!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.70,0:56:47.77,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Even those that goes to the 3rd period can watch this right after
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.02,0:56:51.35,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Please look forward to this as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.35,0:56:53.52,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Well then- Oh there's more huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.52,0:56:58.77,Kokona,,0,0,0,,Next, it's regarding Sakura Gakuin's Ganbare!! FRESH Monday, 2017 Nendo Outdoor School
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.77,0:57:00.77,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,That's last year!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.77,0:57:00.77,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,It's 2018!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.72,0:57:03.22,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You weren't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.85,0:57:05.30,Marin,,0,0,0,,It's 2018
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.75,0:57:12.57,Kokona,,0,0,0,,It'll be broadcasted in two parts which will be on August 27th \Nand September 3rd so be sure to watch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.57,0:57:14.07,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,Please do!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.15,0:57:17.95,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,FRESH Monday is also having tons of interesting development
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.17,0:57:20.92,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,We really went all out today, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.92,0:57:24.00,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Though I do feel like I owe Shintani tons of apologies!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.00,0:57:26.42,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,And of course, towards Fujihira and Nonaka as well
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.60,0:57:28.45,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Let's praise Hidaka for her acting too!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.52,0:57:31.25,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,She was really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.25,0:57:32.67,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,She's really amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.17,0:57:34.60,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I believed her!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.60,0:57:36.40,Kano,,0,0,0,,I honestly believed her!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.25,0:57:40.47,Kano,,0,0,0,,She was so believable when we were in the dressing room!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.70,0:57:43.95,Kano,,0,0,0,,When she said her head hurts, I thought she was sick
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.15,0:57:45.27,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,She has been acting since then
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.77,0:57:48.22,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,That said, I was walking like this since then as well
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.57,0:57:51.97,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Too bad there was no one around!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.55,0:57:51.97,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,We didn't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.55,0:57:54.27,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,How sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.27,0:57:57.05,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's cheer for Asou next week!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.05,0:58:00.20,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,Yes! We'll be watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.20,0:58:02.90,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I hope she'll succeed! Talk Chairperson!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.90,0:58:03.80,Kano,,0,0,0,,Talk Chairperson!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.80,0:58:05.22,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Please do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.37,0:58:08.20,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Now then! Please- Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.20,0:58:11.77,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,We're accepting postcards as well! \NThe theme will be "Summer Plan"
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.77,0:58:12.92,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Summer plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.92,0:58:15.97,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,We'll appreciate it if you would send them!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.97,0:58:19.55,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Those who have their letters read will be given a sticker
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.82,0:58:22.07,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What will be shown after this again?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.47,0:58:27.87,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Well, it's the outdoor school trailer
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.45,0:58:28.82,Marin,,0,0,0,,I forgot! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.82,0:58:30.52,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Hidaka is on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.17,0:58:32.67,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,It's all right
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.90,0:58:33.77,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Thank you
